etomica.virial

Class MCMoveClusterRingRegrowOrientation

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.integrator.mcmove.MCMove
      • etomica.integrator.mcmove.MCMoveBox
        • etomica.virial.MCMoveClusterRingRegrowOrientation

  • public class MCMoveClusterRingRegrowOrientation
extends MCMoveBox
    MCMove that fully regrows the beads of a ring polymer by rotating the images, accepting or rejecting the move based on the sampling weight.
